spec_data.Name: claws-mail-plugins-vcalendar
spec_data.Description:
This plugin enables vCalendar message handling like that produced by
Evolution or Outlook. It also supports subscribing to remote webCal feeds, and
exporting of your meetings or all your calendars.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Sun 17 Sep 2017 05:07:00 PM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Handling of vCalendar messages in Claws Mail
